text: Praproče v Tuhinju () is a small settlement above the Tuhinj Valley in the Municipality of Kamnik in the Upper Carniola region of Slovenia. ==Name== The name of the settlement was changed from Praproče to Praproče v Tuhinju in 1955.Spremembe naselij 1948–95. 1996.
